Our goal is to establish long-term relationships with developers, and we encourage you to contact us before terminating your agreement to see if we can improve your Amazon Appstore Developer Program experience. If you would like to terminate your agreement, please send an email with your developer name, contact information, and a list of your applications to apps-notices@amazon.com with a CC via email to contracts-legal@amazon.com. It can take up to 10 days from our receipt of your email for your account to be officially terminated. All requests to terminate the agreement with Amazon Appstore Developer portal will be final and all sales of your applications within the Amazon Appstore for Android will be suspended. You will have limited access to the Amazon Appstore Developer portal after the agreement has been terminated.
